rows.label: tlk41100122_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I've made up my mind! Even if
Superbia sinks, I'm staying with
my older brother 'til the very end!

rows.label: tlk41100122_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't ever want to leave him all
alone again, like back in Gula!

rows.label: tlk41100122_05_msg0003
rows.name:
From now on, we run together, and
we die together! Right, big bro?!
